{"tid":2462853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢篇新聞稿邊個打，睇到好撚尷尬","createTime":"2021-03-26T09:09:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T12:18:29.000Z","uid":312744,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ba70c6f7ceeb55af82bd8cb762c1f6d9b0432667","tid":2462853,"uid":312744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:09:36.000Z","msg":"配合林二汶紅館演唱會 九巴開辦十一條特別線<br />\n為配合在二零二一年三月二十七至二十八日，紅磡香港體育館舉行林二汶《The Beginning of Faith Live》演唱會，九巴十一條特別路線將於演唱會結束後約十五分鐘起，於館外暢運道停車場（綠閘對開）開出。「無論鐵路會崩壞，方向未會被活埋」，九巴特別線服務覆蓋新界及九龍各區，「緊抱著便去到終端」。各特別線詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.kmb.hk/tc/news/press/archives/news202103263800.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.kmb.hk%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Fpress%2Farchives%2Fnews202103263800.html&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GpKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=58de99ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.kmb.hk/tc/news/press/archives/news202103263800.html</a><br />\n<br />\n尷尬程度直逼李力持級數<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d03e16fd20894d31194f5488ba644a4422fa60c","tid":2462853,"uid":312744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T10:43:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb2b22e71e93e5c9bbf6b56fcd2cb81f41106edb","tid":2462853,"uid":177168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T12:14:44.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"purple\"><strong>狗巴 286C 綫 已擴展至全日服務<br />\n由馬鞍山 第一城 經青沙公路 特快來往深水埗 長沙灣<br />\n全面覆蓋西九龍各大熱點<br />\n第一城來往長沙灣 車程祇需二十分鐘 出行更方便</strong></span>"},{"pid":"cf6c810ad7cf14ea8883dd2691bdc766e86f4cec","tid":2462853,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T12:17:02.000Z","msg":"林二汶歌詞喎"},{"pid":"78e13488610311242af599a04272d44cfa06baaf","tid":2462853,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T12:17:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/so